 222:src/main.cpp  **** // ‚îÄ‚îÄ Voice 6: very closed, dark sub bass ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚î
 223:src/main.cpp  **** //   The opposite of the scream: a deep, muffled power-chord bass. A clean sine
 224:src/main.cpp  **** //   sub carries the weight under a mellow triangle root; the fifth and octave
 225:src/main.cpp  **** //   are dialed right back. The filter sits down around the fundamental and only
 226:src/main.cpp  **** //   creeps open a couple of octaves at full pressure, so it stays dark and
 227:src/main.cpp  **** //   muted ‚Äî felt more than heard. Low resonance, almost no drive.
